high_descs: Turn right step forward, turn left step forward to counter
Pick up spoon next to stove
Turn left step forward, turn right to face sink
put spoon in sink, turn on water then turn off water, then pick up spoon
Turn left and walk towards counter
anns.task_desc: Wash the spoon on the counter and place it on a different counter

high_descs: Go straight, then to the right to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick the spoon up from off of the counter.
Move to the left to face the sink.
Run the water over the spoon and then pick the spoon up from out of the sink.
Turn to the left to face the bread by the corner of the counter.
Place the spoon on the counter to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Place the rinsed spoon on the counter next to the bread.

high_descs: Cross the room to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick the spoon up from the counter.
Turn to the left to face the sink.
Put the fork in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the fork up from the sink.
Turn to the left and face the counter to the left of the bread.
Put the spoon down on the counter to the left of the bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean fork on the counter.
